vements to its environmental record since  when the company began its first formal sustainability efforts in  the ball corporation issued its first sustainability report and began releases subsequent sustainability reports on its website the first report was an accaceres north american sustainability awards cowinner of the best first time reporter award in citation needed in the toxic  list for  using data from  researchers at the university of massachusetts amhersts political economy research institute peri identified the ball corporation as the thlargest corporate producer of air pollution in the united states with an estimated  million pounds of toxic air released annually the peri report for  using data from  ranked the ball corporation th on its toxic  list peris report for  using data from  ranked it th the peri studies indicated major pollutants included glycol ethers and trimethylbenzene the peri toxic  air polluters list for  ranked the ball corporation as  in its list of companies producing the most air pollution in the united states in  newsweek ranked the ball corporation as th in their green  report which reviewed the environmental performances of the  largest publiclytraded companies in the united states notesedit  a b c d e f g ball corporation form k annual report filing date feb   pdf secdatabasecom retrieved feb     ball corporation form k annual report filing date apr   secdatabasecom retrieved feb     a b c d e f g h i j k l barbara quigley the ball brothers in gugin linda c james e st clair eds  indianas  the people who shaped the hoosier state indianapolis indiana historical society press p  isbn    anthony o edmonds e bruce geelhoed  ball state university an interpretive history bloomington in indiana university press p  isbn    philip a africa  keuka college a history valley forge pa judson press pp – oclc    frank clayton ball  memoirs of frank clayton ball muncie in scott printing company pp – oclc    edmund f ball  from fruit jars to satel